Jose Mourinho has got Manchester United fans very excited by accidentally mentioning Alexis Sanchez&rsquo;s name when asked an unrelated question at his post-match press conference.<br />
<br />
When Mourinho was asked by a Spanish journalist if United were attempting to sign Morata, he replied in Spanish: &lsquo;It is a question for Florentino [Perez, the Real president]. I don&rsquo;t know the first thing about Sanchez.&rsquo;
